
*** 0.90 (May 17, 2002)

* Complete rewrite of engine.  See pod for details.
* set_cons_weight is now obsolete.  it is kept for compatibility but is a
    null operation 
* Fixed spelling of exclamation in API
* Fixed misspelling of "source" as "souce" in the docs
* Allow a single werd as output from get_werd
* Updated email address

*** 0.03 (Aug 31 2000)

Fixed bugs in the module that was causing it to use class data for object
methods.  Also fixed set_* functions to allow Silly::Werder::set_*(); syntax

*** 0.02 (Aug 28 2000)

First public version of Silly::Werder
